{"tid":1727909,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔兔食物和份量 !","createTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:07:13.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e435bc0c4d70bd2c60fd18c31ee861659bb092","tid":1727909,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society)</span>:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡😊<br />\n- 2湯匙兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙或以下)水果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更多資訊：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQCRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=a557ebeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"1e1363210360dc001cc39a881cb912c2ae85c99e","tid":1727909,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子生日Party !!</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNfkeOcEHtOk&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQCRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=931dbe1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk</a>"},{"pid":"cd1b91756893e88877821b78b6dc0463bc51305e","tid":1727909,"uid":84581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"人地話食開一隻草唔好轉(same brand, same type)，係咪？"},{"pid":"a9fb82f3db4f5a5e0752a167f1228aa23bedfe64","tid":1727909,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd1b91756893e88877821b78b6dc0463bc51305e","tid":1727909,"uid":84581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"人地話食開一隻草唔好轉(same brand, same type)，係咪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"牌子不轉，但乾草可調教，例如: <br />\n今天Timothy hay, <br />\n明天Orchard hay + Timothy hay<br />\n後天Oat hay +orchard hay"},{"pid":"3430d49db57c470e69f901bc4f0e534529b55b79","tid":1727909,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子吃西瓜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於糖份高，這video分咗幾日比兔仔食。糖份高不宜多吃，否則損害腸胃，患上致命的GI stasis!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSXw7zGeWMhU&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQCRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=f8064f95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU</a>"}]}